<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463425' id='t-463425'>before the age of 18.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465654' id='t-465654'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='473502' id='t-473502'>In my community,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='475243' id='t-475243'>that was the first time a community,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477890' id='t-477890'>they had to call the bylaws,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480351' id='t-480351'>the first bylaw that protected girls</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483858' id='t-483858'>in our community.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486052' id='t-486052'>We did not stop there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487840' id='t-487840'>We forged ahead.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='490789' id='t-490789'>We were determined to fight for girls
not just in my community,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494643' id='t-494643'>but even in other communities.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497429' id='t-497429'>When the child marriage bill
was being presented in February,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501562' id='t-501562'>we were there at the Parliament house.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505208' id='t-505208'>Every day, when the members
of Parliament were entering,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509294' id='t-509294'>we were telling them,
&quot;Would you please support the bill?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512383' id='t-512383'>And we don't have
much technology like here,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517142' id='t-517142'>but we have our small phones.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519139' id='t-519139'>So we said, &quot;Why can't we get 
their numbers and text them?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524178' id='t-524178'>So we did that. It was a good thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527428' id='t-527428'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529448' id='t-529448'>So when the bill passed,
we texted them back,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532421' id='t-532421'>&quot;Thank you for supporting the bill.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534849' id='t-534849'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535919' id='t-535919'>And when the bill was signed
by the president,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='539264' id='t-539264'>making it into law, it was a plus.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542630' id='t-542630'>Now, in Malawi, 18 is the legal
