<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548482' id='t-548482'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='554495' id='t-554495'>It's a good thing to know
that the bill passed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='558071' id='t-558071'>but let me tell you this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561113' id='t-561113'>There are countries where 18
