<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589951' id='t-589951'>We don't have to be subjected as second,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593712' id='t-593712'>but they have to know that women,
as we are in this room,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597950' id='t-597950'>we are not just women,
we are not just girls,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='601000' id='t-601000'>we are extraordinary.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602980' id='t-602980'>We can do more.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='604893' id='t-604893'>And another thing for Malawi,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607888' id='t-607888'>and not just Malawi but other countries:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='610790' id='t-610790'>The laws which are there,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='614575' id='t-614575'>you know how a law is not a law
