<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='630387' id='t-630387'>at the community level,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632570' id='t-632570'>where girls' issues are very striking.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637956' id='t-637956'>Girls face issues, difficult issues,
