</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:08
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657254' id='t-657254'>And another thing I would say is that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='661363' id='t-661363'>girls' voices and women's voices</span>
